title: Shocker Internet Drive In Week 9 - "Horror Head" Double Feature

sources.title: Shocker Internet Drive In Week 9 - "Horror Head" Double Feature
sources.description: Even though one of our past features was removed because someone after the fact determined that a movie was still copyrighted even though it was posted elsewhere on the archive, we will not be sidetracked! This week, we strongly suggest you get a good parking slot for our "Horror Head" Double Feature. After a hearty welcome and a classic Thanksgiving cartoon, we proudly present the 1959 gore classic "The Brain That Wouldn't Die", which is followed by a brief intermission and then "The Head", more or less the German version of our first film.
